bayou.jtype

Class PrimitiveType<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • bayou.jtype.JavaType<T>
      • bayou.jtype.PrimitiveType<T>

  • public final class PrimitiveType<T>
extends JavaType<T>
    Primitive type.

    `T` is the boxed type of the primitive type, for example 

         PrimitiveType<Boolean> type_boolean = PrimitiveType.of(boolean.class);
